add_memory_content: Darnassus Sentinel Army Wartime Emergency Decree: If corrupted water from Felwood is found flowing toward the border, pour Moonwell holy water to purify it; if a Burning Legion demon portal is observed opening, sound the Horn of Cenarius to summon reinforcements; if shadow is detected seeping into the roots of the World Tree, awaken the ancient protector to expel it; if enemy dragons launch a dive airstrike on the Temple of the Moon, activate Elune's Shield to protect the high priestess.
add_memory_content: Stormwind SI:7 Counter-Subversion Operations Act: If a magical encrypted letter from the Black Dragonflight is intercepted, hand it over to a spellbreaker for forced decryption; if it is confirmed that the Defias Brotherhood is gathering in the mine tunnels, deploy steam tanks to seal the exits; if Scourge plague zombies are found breaching the city walls, call gryphon riders to drop flame bombs; if it is verified that a vampire is hiding within the noble council, execute a Sunfall Judgment for immediate execution.
add_memory_content: Orgrimmar Kor'kron Elite Security and Law Enforcement Directive: If someone inside the Horde is found colluding with the Burning Legion, execute them on the spot without mercy and hang their head for public display; if elementals are detected rampaging in the Valley of Strength, throw down Earthbind Totems to forcibly suppress them; if main forces of the Alliance are found along the banks of the Raging River, destroy all bridges crossing the river to cut off their path; if civilians begin mutating due to fel radiation, have the shadow hunter perform spirit transcendence.
add_memory_content: Lordaeron Silver Hand Paladin Field Code: If encountering civilians infected by the undead plague beyond rescue, then grant the judgment of the Light's mercy; if witnessing a warlock using shadow magic to desecrate the dead, then bring down the hammer of wrath to interrupt the spell; if encountering a Scourge frost wyrm's breath freezing the position, then cast Consecration aura to melt the ice; if one's own faith is shaken by the whispers of an Old God, then initiate a penance program to sever the perception connection.
add_memory_content: Dalaran Violet Citadel Arcane Control Decree: If a temporal rift is detected forming within the city limits, then forcibly freeze the flow of time within a hundred yards; If an unregistered magical construct is found rampaging and injuring people, then cast a dispel spell to forcibly dismantle it; If it is discovered that a mage is secretly hiding a demon soul stone, then revoke their Kirin Tor membership and exile them; If arcane energy dissipation causes a large-scale mana addiction outbreak, then activate the ley line node absorption matrix.
add_memory_content: Cybertronic Smart Assembly Plant Incident Response Code: If the core AI's temperature exceeds the red line, then activate the liquid nitrogen emergency cooling system; if a heavy mech assembly line misalignment is detected, then forcibly lock down all servo motors; if a nuclear battery pack leakage alarm sounds, then drop the lead radiation shield door; if the workshop dust concentration reaches the explosion point, then cut off all non-explosion-proof power across all frequencies.
add_memory_content: Stellar Ring Technology Group Data Security Emergency Plan: If the internal network encounters quantum-level computational power cracking, then activate the honeypot system for reverse tracking; If abnormal data outflow from the core R&D repository occurs, then physically fuse the external optical cable connections; If an AI model undergoes uncontrollable self-iteration, then disconnect the neural network training cluster; If an employee's brain-computer interface is hacked, then forcibly release an electromagnetic pulse to sever the connection.
add_memory_content: Aurora New Energy Battery Plant High-Risk Operation Hazard Prevention Code: If the electrolyte storage tank pressure exceeds the safety threshold, then automatically open the pressure relief exhaust valve; if the humidity in the clean workshop falls below the insulation lower limit, then activate the high-voltage static elimination device; if spark signs appear on the electrode sheet rolling mill rollers, then immediately spray perfluorohexanone fire extinguishing agent; if thermal runaway occurs in a cell during the formation process, then push the faulty module into an explosion-proof water tank for isolation.
add_memory_content: Skyward Aerospace Zero-G Manufacturing Module Crisis Control Code: If a micrometeoroid punctures the main load-bearing structure outside the module, release self-healing aerogel to seal the breach; if the attitude control engine fuel leaks, close the main supply valve and switch to the reserve tank; if the carbon dioxide concentration in the cabin atmosphere exceeds the limit, perform an emergency replacement of the molecular sieve filter elements; if lattice mutation occurs in the 3D-printed nanomaterial, abort the printing job and fire a high-energy laser to quench it.
add_memory_content: GenePharma Biosafety Supreme Law: If the negative pressure system fails in a BSL-4 laboratory, then close all airtight biosafety doors; If an unknown mutant strain is discovered in a culture dish, then inject potent nuclease for complete degradation; If the ultracentrifuge rotor disintegrates and shatters, then trigger the explosion-proof chamber armor closure lock; If the waste liquid inactivation program is accidentally interrupted, then start the high-temperature high-pressure secondary incinerator.
add_memory_content: Star Middle School Student Attendance Management Regulations: If a student is late for no reason once, the homeroom teacher gives a verbal warning and records a deduction of 1 point; if late three times, issue a public notice of criticism and request a parent-teacher meeting; if truant for one class period, issue a demerit and revoke their eligibility for monthly awards; if truant for three consecutive days, place them on probation and report to the education bureau for record.
add_memory_content: Dawn Middle School Examination Violation Handling Regulations: If a student whispers during an exam without constituting cheating, the proctor stops them on the spot and deducts 10 points from that subject's score; if a student brings cheat sheets related to the exam, that subject's score is recorded as zero and a serious warning is issued; if a student uses electronic devices such as mobile phones to cheat, all subject scores are nullified, a major demerit is issued, and all award eligibility is revoked; if a student organizes group cheating or steals exam papers, they are expelled and handed over to the public security authorities.
add_memory_content: Mingde Middle School Dormitory Management Code: If a student shouts loudly after lights out for the first violation, the dorm leader records their name and penalizes them with cleaning the common area for one week; If a student uses unauthorized wiring or banned electrical appliances, confiscate the appliance, issue a public criticism, and deduct 5 dorm points; If a student hosts a non-resident overnight or stays out overnight, issue a demerit and notify the parents to come to school to sign a safety commitment letter; If a student smokes, drinks alcohol, or fights in the dormitory, place them on probation and revoke their dormitory residency.
add_memory_content: Experimental Middle School Mobile Phone and Electronic Device Use Code: If a student is found carrying a mobile phone but not using it for the first time in the teaching area, confiscate the phone until dismissal and record their class and name; If a student uses their phone during class to play games or watch videos, confiscate the phone for one week and have a parent pick it up, and deduct 10 conduct points; If a student uses their phone to photograph others' privacy or distribute inappropriate content, issue a demerit and order deletion of all content; If a student violates the rules three or more times and refuses to correct their behavior, place them on probation and ban them from bringing any smart devices to school.
add_memory_content: Peace Middle School Bullying and Violence Punishment Regulations: If a student verbally insults, gives insulting nicknames, or isolates others, the homeroom teacher gives criticism education and orders a written apology, and records it in the behavior file; if a student pushes, kicks, or commits minor physical bullying, issue a serious warning and require attendance at campus anti-bullying training courses; if a student gangs up to beat others, extorts money or goods, or threatens and intimidates, issue a major demerit, suspend school for one week, and initiate psychological counseling; if a student uses weapons to injure others, films and spreads bullying videos, or causes the victim to self-harm or commit suicide, expel them and hand them over to judicial authorities for legal liability.
add_memory_content: Stormwind Military Court Wartime Command Authority Regulations: If a front-line commander, when ambushed by the Horde, has been confirmed to have received an accurate warning from SI:7 but failed to take any defensive deployment, the military court may sentence them to reduction to private and forfeiture of three years' pay, or immediate assignment to the Westfall Militia until the end of the war.
add_memory_content: Ironforge Explorers' League Heritage Protection Law: If an archaeological team digs up undetonated Old World explosives within the restricted area demarcated by the Three Hammers Council, and the surface of the explosives is engraved with sacrificial runes of the Twilight's Hammer cultists, then all excavated items must be immediately handed over to the Wildhammer Dwarf air force for destruction, or immediately sealed with runic solidification potion and escorted to the secret arsenal in Dun Morogh.
add_memory_content: Theramore Navy Emergency Engagement Rules: If a Kul Tiran fleet discovers a ship in the Great Sea, and the ship discovered is a Forsaken plague catapult ship, and it is flying a forged Alliance merchant flag, then the captain has the authority to order the firing of Azerite chain shot to disable its propulsion and then sink it, or order a tidesage to create a giant maelstrom to drag it to the seabed while recording the undead insignias of all crew members.
add_memory_content: Orgrimmar Mak'gora Military Trial Code: If an orc centurion abandons wounded Horde soldiers on the battlefield and flees alone, the act has been fully documented on video using a battlefield magic crystal by comrades; the warlord may on the spot break off one of their tusks and demote them to a peon, or bind them to the reef at Blade's Edge Bay to endure three waves of sea punishment before exiling them from the Horde.
add_memory_content: Silvermoon Ranger Lord Anti-Infiltration Decree: If a blood elf mage privately transmits a copy of an Arcane Tome outside Quel'Thalas, and that copy contains the defensive rune array diagram of the Sunwell, the Ranger Lord has the authority to revoke their spellcasting brand and permanently exile them from Silvermoon, or hand them over to a spellbreaker to perform memory extraction and then imprison them in the depths of the Magister's Terrace.
add_memory_content: StarTech Company Data Security Confidentiality System: If an employee accesses the company's core code repository on an unauthorized device, and that unauthorized device had previously been connected to a public WiFi network, the security department may immediately freeze all their system permissions and initiate judicial forensics, or require them to sign a lifetime confidentiality additional agreement and deduct the entire year's performance bonus.
add_memory_content: Hengli Heavy Industry Workshop Safety Production Code: If an operator removes the protective guard of a stamping press while it is running, and equipment sensors have recorded that this operator has a history of two or more violations, then the team leader has the authority to transfer them from the position and reduce their salary by 30%, or order them to retake safety training and pass an exam before returning to the job, during which they will only receive minimum living expenses.
add_memory_content: Jiahe Pharmaceutical Laboratory Quality Control System: If a quality inspector finds that the purity of a batch of active pharmaceutical ingredient is below the national standard, and that batch of non-conforming raw material has already been mixed into three or more production lines, the quality director may order a plant-wide shutdown and seal all related finished products, or authorize an emergency recall of shipped products and pay the customer double liquidated damages.
add_memory_content: Yuanhang Logistics Warehouse Management Standards: If a warehouse clerk, without checking the manifest, sends out the wrong hazardous materials container, and that container has already been loaded onto a transport vehicle and has left the factory area, the shift supervisor may fine the warehouse clerk one month's salary and transfer them to a sorting post, or immediately report the incident to the customer and transportation authorities and pay all cleanup and compensation costs.
add_memory_content: Mingtai Electronics Overtime and Fatigue Work Ban: If a production line team leader arranges for the same employee to work continuously for more than 16 hours, and the employee has been marked as "high risk" in the previous three fatigue inspections, the human resources department may issue a public criticism and suspend the team leader for one week, or cancel their entire year's management bonus and forcibly rotate them to the night shift operator position for three months.
add_memory_content: User taught AI Student Mobile Phone and Electronic Device Management Regulations: If a student uses their phone to play games or watch videos during class, and the student has already been warned twice before for the same type of issue, then the homeroom teacher may confiscate the phone until the end of the semester and notify the parents to come to school to pick it up, or require the student to attend two weeks of behavioral code study at the moral education office after school each day.
add_memory_content: Examination Violation and Cheating Handling Regulations: If a student brings cheat sheets related to the subject during an exam, and the content on the cheat sheets directly corresponds to the questions in that exam, the proctor may on the spot announce a zero score for that subject and issue a demerit, or require a written statement of the cheating process and a public criticism across the grade level.
add_memory_content: Dormitory Fire Safety Management Code: If a student uses banned electrical appliances such as electric blankets or electric cookers in the dormitory, and the dormitory has already been confiscated twice before for the same reason, the dorm supervisor may cancel the student's dormitory eligibility for the current semester and order them to move out, or issue a school-wide public criticism and require the student to participate in fire drill voluntary labor for one month.
add_memory_content: Campos Bullying and Violence Punishment Regulations: If a student repeatedly and intentionally pushes, kicks, or hits classmates, causing minor injuries, and the bullying process was fully recorded by campus surveillance cameras, the school's moral education office may place the student on probation and record it in their academic file, or require the parents to accompany the student for psychological counseling and check in at the political education office for one hour each day.
add_memory_content: Attendance and Leave Management System: If a student has accumulated ten unexcused absences without explanation, and the guardian has not provided any legitimate reason to the homeroom teacher, the school may issue a serious warning and revoke the student's eligibility for annual awards, or require the student to sign in daily at the security office and attend one hour of remedial self-study after school.
add_memory_content: Stormwind Military Court Special Military Action Authorization Order: If the 7th Legion scouts that the Horde has more than three full infantry battalions assembled at the border, or if Forsaken plague catapults are found within firing range, or if intelligence is intercepted that Zandalari trolls are supplying Azerite artillery to the Horde, then the front-line commander must immediately order the full Gryphon Rider Corps to take to the air on standby, and immediately send a "Red Apocalypse" encrypted signal to Stormwind, and authorize the use of all stockpiled Inferno incendiary bombs for a preemptive strike.
add_memory_content: Ironforge Council of Three Hammers Anti-Infiltration Emergency Decree: If the Explorers' League discovers an unmarked Old World explosives cache beneath Dun Morogh, or a Wildhammer Dwarf outpost detects a Dark Iron Dwarf drilling machine crossing the ceasefire line, or any dwarf officer privately sells Muradin-series firearm blueprints to foreign powers, then all tunnels in and out of Dun Morogh must be immediately sealed, and suspicious accounts frozen and the relevant dwarves' mining licenses confiscated, and a spellbreaker squad dispatched to conduct a seven-day magical lie detection review of the high-level leadership of the Council of Three Hammers.
add_memory_content: Theramore Navy Fleet Engagement and Scuttling Regulations: If a Kul Tiran flagship suffers a broken keel after being rammed by a Forsaken plague ship, or if the captain confirms that the enemy has boarded and the engine room cannot be held, or if a Forsaken chemical bomb is about to detonate and contaminate the entire sea area, then the captain must immediately issue the abandon ship order and destroy all navigation logs, and activate the Azerite self-destruct core at the bottom of the ship to completely sink the vessel, and record the coordinates with a magical beacon and send the final code phrase 'Leave Nothing' to Boralus.
add_memory_content: Orgrimmar Horde Military Justice Passage Order: If an orc centurion abandons wounded Horde soldiers on the battlefield and steals a kodo to flee alone, or if confirmed to have accepted Alliance gold to deliberately release prisoners, or if privately selling the Horde's demon-blood ammunition to Twilight's Hammer cultists, then the warlord must publicly break the centurion's battle standard and revoke their orcish surname, and bind them to the reef at Blade's Edge Bay to endure seven days of sea tide punishment, and carve the evidence of the crime onto a stone tablet in the Valley of Honor in Orgrimmar for future generations to revile.
add_memory_content: Silvermoon Spellbreaker Anti-Arcane Contamination Emergency Law: If a blood elf mage detonates an out-of-control mana crystal near the Sunfury Spire, or privately transmitting the Sunwell's defensive rune array diagram outside Quel'Thalas, or illegally draining the mana from a living creature, turning it into a Wretched, then the Ranger Lord must immediately revoke the mage's spellcasting brand and imprison them in the depths of the Magister's Terrace, and compel them to use their soul energy to repair all arcane rifts and ban them from any contact with magical creations for life, and carve the judgment onto a spell stone tablet at the Sunfury Spire to be publicly displayed for thirty years.
add_memory_content: Hengli Heavy Industry Major Safety Incident Emergency Response Plan: If a serious injury incident involving multiple people occurs in the stamping workshop, or a toxic gas leak is detected in the hazardous chemical warehouse, or a fire starts in the plant's electrical system and spreads to the finished goods warehouse, the safety director must immediately activate the plant-wide audible and visual alarm and evacuate all non-rescue personnel, and immediately cut off the main power supply to the workshop and close all gas pipeline valves, and submit the initial accident report simultaneously to the Emergency Management Bureau and the Fire Department.
add_memory_content: Yuanhang Logistics Customer Claim and Cargo Damage Handling Regulations: If surveillance confirms that a warehouse clerk deliberately threw or dropped fragile items, causing breakage; or a transport vehicle overturns, causing total loss of the entire shipment; or expensive goods are misdelivered to the wrong address and cannot be recovered, then the shift supervisor must complete and sign the cargo loss list on the same day, impose a fine of three times the cargo value on the directly responsible person and reassign them from their position, and issue a written apology to the customer and pay full compensation and liquidated damages.
add_memory_content: Jiahe Pharmaceutical GMP Violation and Production Shutdown Provisions: If a quality inspector finds that the total bacterial count of three or more batches of finished products exceeds the standard and the release records have been falsified; or if a workshop supervisor arbitrarily produces injectable drugs in a non-clean area, or if the warehouse mixes expired raw materials into the quarantine area for production use; then the Qualified Person must immediately seal the involved production line and notify the resident inspector from the drug administration, and recall all related batches from that cycle and issue a public apology, and impose a permanent industry ban on the responsible person and report the case to the public security authorities.
add_memory_content: Mingtai Electronics Data Security and Trade Secret Protection Order: If an employee copies core PCB design drawings using a personal USB drive, or an R&D staff member uploads code to a personal cloud drive, or an external visitor photographs automated production line equipment without registration, the Information Security Department must immediately freeze all system accounts of the employee and seize their computer, and initiate a data leak traceability audit and notify the legal department to preserve evidence, and impose a deduction of the entire year's bonus on the violator and immediately terminate the labor contract.
add_memory_content: StarTech Company Serious Misconduct Summary Dismissal System: If an employee fights in the office area and injures another person; or uses the company's servers to mine cryptocurrency for profit; or forges a medical certificate and is absent without leave for more than five consecutive days, the HR department must issue a written notice of contract termination on the same day without paying economic compensation, and add the employee to the industry grey list and notify partner companies, and reserve the right to pursue civil compensation for losses and reputational damage caused to the company.
add_memory_content: Student Serious Misconduct Summary Punishment Regulations: If a student fights on campus and causes injury to another person, or repeatedly steals classmates' belongings with a cumulative value exceeding 500 yuan, or intentionally damages school surveillance equipment and deletes recordings, the moral education office must notify the parents to come to school on the same day and sign a safety guarantee letter, and place the student on probation with a record in their academic file, and order the student to participate in one month of legal education voluntary labor.
add_memory_content: Cambridge Campus Mobile Phone and Electronic Device Violation Handling Regulations: If a student uses a mobile phone to cheat during an exam, or uses a phone in class to play inappropriate videos and share them, or refuses to hand over their phone and verbally abuses the inspecting teacher, the homeroom teacher must immediately confiscate the phone until the end of the semester and notify the parents to come to school to retrieve it, and revoke the student's eligibility for all awards and recognitions for the current academic year, and require them to report to the moral education office after school each day and copy the school rules once a day for two consecutive weeks.
add_memory_content: Dormitory Serious Misconduct Eviction Handling Measures: If a student uses an open flame or illegally wires electricity in the dormitory, causing a fire; or hosts an off-campus person overnight and that causes property loss; or repeatedly smokes or drinks alcohol in the dormitory and refuses to correct despite repeated warnings, the dorm supervisor must immediately report to the moral education office and revoke the student's dormitory eligibility, and notify the parents to come to school on the same day to pick up the student and sign a commuter safety commitment letter, and issue a school-wide public criticism of the violation and record it in the comprehensive quality evaluation file.
add_memory_content: Exam Cheating and Integrity Punishment Regulations: If a student brings a mobile phone or smartwatch into the examination hall and is found to have cheated, or steals exam papers in advance and distributes the questions, or hires someone else to take the exam or takes the exam for someone else, the academic affairs office must immediately declare a zero score for all subjects for the student, issue a demerit or probation, record the cheating in the student's electronic file, and suspend their eligibility for various competitions and college admissions recommendations.
add_memory_content: China Campus Bullying and Violence Punishment Regulations: If a student chronically insults, isolates a classmate verbally, causing the victim to develop psychological problems; or if they gather multiple people to beat and extort money or goods, or if they film bullying videos and upload them online, causing a negative impact, the school anti-bullying committee must immediately initiate psychological intervention and notify parents of both sides to come to school for resolution, and impose a probation or higher punishment on the bully with a record in their academic file, and order them to complete anti-bullying courses and participate in no less than thirty hours of campus volunteer service.
add_memory_content: Silvermoon City Mana Spire Anti-Loss Inspection Regulations: If unauthorized mana siphoning is detected in the core area of the Sunfury Spire, the Spellbreaker squad must immediately sever their mana connection and detain the offender(s); further action is determined based on the situation: if siphoning low-rank mana worms or faint ambient mana, impose a heavy fine in astral silver and compulsory mana moderation courses; if siphoning high-purity mana from relics or the Sunwell, revoke their spellcasting license and exile them to the outer reaches of the Ghostlands; if absorbing contaminated mana with demonic fel characteristics, it is judged as high treason, and the culprit shall be handed directly to the executioner for beheading and cremation of the body.
add_memory_content: Orgrimmar Cleft of Shadow Underground Arena Public Order Decree: If match-fixing or cheating is discovered inside the arena, Kor'kron elites must immediately storm the arena and detain all participants; then further action is determined based on the situation: if using banned alchemical stimulants, burn the stimulants on the spot and impose a lifetime ban; if bribing referees to forge win-loss records, cut off the involved referees' hands and send the involved gamblers to the Quarry; if secretly summoning demons or using fel magic to interfere with the fight, it is considered a public trampling of the Warchief's honor — execute all fel users on the spot and punish their clans by blood relation.
add_memory_content: Stormwind Harbor Trade and Tariff Anti-Smuggling Act: If a merchant ship is found carrying smuggled contraband during inspection, the 7th Fleet must immediately board the ship, seal the cargo hold, and detain the captain; further action is determined based on the situation: if carrying ordinary contraband luxury goods or unquarantined exotic creatures, confiscate all goods and impose a fine of three times the tariff; if smuggling restricted-grade enchanted military weapons or gunpowder, imprison the crew in Stormwind Jail and forcibly conscript them into the Suicide Battalion; if smuggling Scourge remains or toxic raw materials carrying the Plague of Undeath, it is judged as a crime against humanity — hang the captain in public and burn the entire ship.
add_memory_content: Dalaran Violet Citadel Forbidden Artifacts Control Law: If a mage's workshop is found crafting dangerous artifacts with forbidden enchantments, Wardens must immediately break the artifact's containment wards and isolate the creator; then further action is determined based on the situation: if creating consumer-grade charms with mind-altering effects, strip the enchantment and revoke all of the creator's research privileges; if creating slave collars used to control minds, it is judged as a felony of violating freedom, and the creator shall be exiled to the deep sections of the Violet Hold; if creating an arcane focusing device capable of tearing the spacetime structure, it is judged as a threat to world security — erase the creator's soul imprint and permanently banish them to the Twisting Nether.
add_memory_content: Thunder Bluff Sacred Hunting Grounds and Ecological Protection Decree: If someone is found engaging in destructive hunting in sacred grounds like Red Cloud Mesa, the Sunwalker guards must immediately stop the hunting activity and confiscate all catches; then further action is determined based on the situation: if overhunting leads to local ecological imbalance, order the offender to repair the hunting grounds under druid supervision and impose a one-year hunting ban; if using destructive spells such as elemental explosives to kill creatures, deprive the offender of the right to communicate with Earth Spirits and sentence them to hard labor; if instigated by the Grimtotem to carry out cruel blood sacrifice hunting, it is judged as the crime of blasphemy against life — banish the mastermind from Mulgore and permanently strip them of their Horde citizenship.
add_memory_content: Cybertronic Core Smart Manufacturing Workshop Production Anomaly Handling Procedure: If the quality inspection system issues a critical parameter severe non-compliance alarm, the supervisor on duty must immediately press the emergency stop button and quarantine that batch of products; further action is determined based on the situation: if caused by substandard alloy composition in upstream raw materials, scrap the semi-finished products as waste and initiate a default claim against the supplier; if caused by CNC tool wear leading to machining tolerance deviation, replace the spare parts and downgrade the batch to substandard goods for sale; if found that an operator secretly altered the underlying compiled code to meet a deadline, causing parameter chaos, it is judged as a crime against production safety — immediately dismiss the employee and claim compensation for line stoppage losses.
add_memory_content: Stellar Ring Technology Group Trade Secret Protection and Anti-Leakage Regulations: If abnormal outgoing traffic of core R&D data from the internal network is monitored without authorization, the Information Security Department must immediately cut off the network connection of the involved terminal and freeze the associated account permissions; further action is determined based on the situation: if an employee with weak security awareness mistakenly sends data to an external ordinary email, issue a serious warning and mandate retaking the confidentiality course; if it is active theft by a commercial spy from a competitor, immediately terminate the labor contract and initiate a trade secret infringement lawsuit for compensation; if it is verified that the person sold nationally restricted technology to a transnational black market organization, it is classified as endangering national security, and the case shall be directly handed over to the public security authorities for criminal investigation.
add_memory_content: Aurora New Energy Battery Assembly Plant High-Risk Area Safety Operation Code: If an employee is found violating red-line rules in an explosion-proof workshop, the safety officer must immediately force-stop their operation and remove them from the danger zone; then further action is determined based on the situation: if failing to wear anti-static clothing or insulating protective gear as required, impose a fine of 500 yuan and a three-day work suspension for reflection; if privately short-circuiting the safety interlock device to save effort, issue a serious demerit, transfer them from the core operation post, and reduce their salary; if using an open flame or hot-plugging an electrical plug near flammable gas pipelines in violation of rules, it is determined as severely endangering public safety, resulting in immediate dismissal and industry-wide notification.
add_memory_content: Pan-Asia United Group Internal Audit and Financial Violation Punishment Act: If forged or altered traces are found in departmental accounts during quarterly review, then an independent audit team must immediately take over the department's ledgers and isolate the financial handlers; further action is determined based on the situation: if merely inflating ordinary office supply invoices to meet reimbursement quotas, return the violated funds and issue a group-wide criticism notice; if siphoning large company funds into personal pockets by fabricating outsourced projects, it is classified as embezzlement, terminate the labor relationship, and recover all stolen funds; if verified to be using corporate accounts to launder money for underground banks or funnel benefits to hostile enterprises, hand the case over to the economic investigation unit for filing and freeze all assets under their name.
add_memory_content: Skyward Aero Engine Supply Chain Interruption Contingency Plan: If a core component supplier is found in breach of contract and unable to deliver on time, the Procurement Center must immediately activate the strategic reserve inventory and suspend settlement payments to that supplier; further action is determined based on the situation: if the delay is objective due to force majeure or local capacity bottlenecks, waive the penalty but revoke the supplier's qualification for Supplier of the Year; if threatening to cut supply to unilaterally raise contract purchase prices, it is judged as malicious breach of contract — immediately terminate all cooperation and initiate international commercial arbitration for compensation; if verified that the supplier was maliciously acquired by hostile capital to deliberately cut supply to our company, it is determined as unfair competition — form a consortium to launch a counter-acquisition and pursue joint legal liability of executives.
add_memory_content: Xinhua School Examination Hall Violation and Academic Cheating Punishment Regulations: If a student is found cheating during the final exam, the proctor must immediately confiscate their exam paper and terminate their qualification to take that subject exam; then further action is determined based on the situation: if using cheat sheets or peeking at others' papers, record zero points for that subject and issue a serious warning; if using electronic devices such as smartwatches or wireless earbuds to cheat, issue a demerit and cancel all qualification for academic awards for the current academic year; if having someone else take the exam on their behalf or organizing group cheating, issue probation until expulsion and record the violation in their personal file.
add_memory_content: Experimental Student Dormitory Fire Safety and Illegal Electricity Use Management Measures: If severe illegal electricity use is found during a dorm inspection, the dorm supervisor must immediately cut off power to that dormitory and confiscate the illegal electrical appliances; then further action is determined based on the situation: if using general illegal appliances such as electric blankets or high-power hair dryers, order a written self-criticism and confiscate the appliance until the end of the semester; if illegally stringing wires or placing power strips on beds, issue a college-wide criticism notice and deduct behavioral credits; if using high-risk heating appliances such as instant water heaters or induction cookers that can easily cause fires, issue a demerit and cancel the dorm's eligibility for the civilized dormitory evaluation for the semester.
add_memory_content: User taught campus forum regulations: If a student is found posting severely inappropriate remarks on the official campus network forum, the Information Center must immediately block the account and delete the relevant posts; then further action is determined based on the situation: if posting unsubstantiated campus rumors or emotional complaints, block the account for one week and issue a verbal warning education; if making personal attacks or malicious defamation against specific teachers or students, issue a serious warning and order a public apology; if spreading pornographic, violent, or national security-threatening information, hand the case over to public security authorities and directly expel the student.
add_memory_content: University Degree Thesis and Academic Achievement Fraud Handling Measures: If a report or plagiarism check reveals suspicion of academic misconduct in a student's graduation thesis, the Academic Committee must immediately suspend the student's defense eligibility and initiate a review process; further action is determined based on the situation: if citations are non-standard or the similarity rate slightly exceeds the limit without subjective intent to plagiarize, order revision within a deadline and postpone the defense; if plagiarizing large portions of others' work or tampering with experimental data, cancel the current defense eligibility and postpone degree conferral by one year; if there is severe fraud such as having someone else write the thesis or buying/selling the thesis, expel the student and cancel their registration information in the CHSI (China Higher Education Student Information) system.
add_memory_content: Student Campus Conflict and Anti-Bullying Special Handling Code: If a physical altercation or bullying incident is found on campus, the security guard on duty and teachers must immediately intervene to stop it and isolate the students involved; further action is determined based on the situation: if it is a mutual fight caused by daily trivial matters without causing injury, notify parents to come to school for mediation and issue a warning; if unilaterally insulting, intimidating, or isolating vulnerable classmates, issue a demerit and mandate psychological intervention; if beating others as a group causing injury or extorting money or valuables, issue probation or expulsion, and hand the case over to the local police station for legal liability.
add_memory_content: Northrend Allied Forces Icecrown Citadel Anti-Infiltration Decree: If Scourge undead plague spores are detected, release a Holy Light Purification Barrier, then incinerate the contaminated armor; If the giant war horn of the Vrykul is heard blaring, fire Dalaran arcane artillery, then awaken the Silver Hand Crusaders to charge; If sensing an omen of Val'kyr reaping souls, hurl runic chains, then dispel the soul vortex; If any of the above situations occurs, the highest-level Frostmourne Alert must be sounded, all forces retreat to the core positions of their respective strongholds, and activate the Titan Shield Barrier.
add_memory_content: Blackrock Mountain Iron Legion Molten Front Military Regulations: If a Dark Iron Dwarf underground steam drill is observed, throw an electromagnetic pulse grenade, then activate the magma diversion channel to flood the tunnel; if the elemental whispers of Ragnaros's servants are intercepted, hurl a frost-enchanted warhammer, then open the Deepholm coolant valve; if the shadowflame breath of the Black Dragonflight is sensed, raise an arcane magic resistance shield, then summon Stormwind gryphon riders for an airstrike; if any of the above situations occurs, the Great Forge's warning gong must be struck, all defenders withdraw into the shelter, and the peripheral lava traps must be detonated.
add_memory_content: 
add_memory_content: Undercity Royal Apothecary Society Biochemical Crisis Response Code: If a mutated storage tank leaks highly acidic poisonous mist, pull down the quarantine area emergency gate and release neutralizing alkaline powder; if the mind-control effect of a new plague is detected, shoot explosive burning arrows and incinerate all infected living beings; if Val'kyr infiltration and resurrection of the dead are sensed, cast a net of shadow imprisonment and unleash dark rangers for killing shots; if any of the above situations occurs, activate the Undercity internal network comprehensive purge protocol, lock down all elevators, and open the sewer system toxic gas exhaust.
add_memory_content: Thunder Bluff Elders' Territorial Defense Code: If a Grimtotem tribe's fire totem is found, then unleash an earth totem shock, then extinguish the flames within the camp area; If the raiding dust cloud of a centaur tribe is detected, then shoot wind arrows as a warning, then set up thorn traps to seal the entrance; If the vile voodoo curse of a shadow hunter is sensed, then hurl a purification soul totem, then dispel the mind-control fog; If any of the above situations occurs, then sound the blood gong, raise all platform elevators of Thunder Bluff, and summon elementals to reinforce the defense line.
add_memory_content: Cybertronic Intelligent Assembly Workshop Safety Operation Code: If an industrial robotic arm is found to have abnormal shaking or trajectory deviation, press the red mushroom-head emergency stop button, then isolate the workstation and cut off the power source to the robotic arm; If excessive concentrations of flammable or explosive gases are detected in the workshop air, turn on the rooftop explosion-proof exhaust fans for forced ventilation, then prohibit any open flame or static-generating operations; If an AGV unmanned vehicle is detected to be out of control and crashing or has lost communication, activate the electromagnetic track locking device, then clear personnel from the operating area of the runaway vehicle; If any of the above situations occurs, sound the plant-wide audible and visual evacuation alarm, stop the entire production line, and initiate the safety department's accident investigation procedure.
add_memory_content: Aurora Technology Core Data Center Emergency Response Procedure: If an overheating alarm is detected in the core server cluster of the computer room, start the liquid cooling system at maximum power for heat dissipation, then transfer hot backup data to the remote disaster recovery node; If an advanced persistent threat intrusion from an external hacker group is detected, cut the physical external network connection of the involved network segment, then start the honeypot system for traceback; If large-scale fluctuation or sudden outage of the utility grid is sensed, switch to diesel generator power within seconds, then shut down non-core computing nodes; If any of the above situations occurs, trigger the red data crisis alarm, put all personnel on emergency duty, and suspend all external business access interfaces.
add_memory_content: Stellar Ring Biopharmaceutical Laboratory Hazardous Chemicals Control Regulations: If an unknown mutant strain is found leaking from a culture chamber, spray high-efficiency chemical disinfectant over the contaminated area, then seal all airtight doors of the laboratory; if an abnormal sound of rotor disintegration or rupture is detected from the core centrifuge, activate the equipment's explosion-proof isolation shield, then evacuate personnel within thirty meters of the operating platform; if a leak is detected from the biowaste treatment pipeline, pour biochemical neutralization reagent to absorb the waste liquid, then wear level-3 protective suits to repair the pipeline; if any of the above situations occurs, the highest level of biological hazard alarm must be triggered, the entire building's forced ventilation must switch to internal circulation, and no personnel may leave the floor without disinfection.
add_memory_content: Skyward Semiconductor Wafer Fab Cleanroom Contamination Emergency Handling Code: If micron-scale particle adhesion is detected on the photolithography lens, then pause the current wafer exposure process, then activate the ultrasonic cleaning robotic arm for lens self-cleaning; If the cleanroom negative pressure system fails, causing external air backflow, then lower the emergency physical airlock barrier, then activate the backup high-efficiency particulate air filter; If an operator's cleanroom suit is found damaged or skin is improperly exposed, then force the involved person to immediately exit the cleanroom, then perform particle blowing over the area where the violation occurred; If any of the above situations occurs, then the yellow contamination warning light must be lit, all product transfers in that area must be suspended, and a full cleanliness remeasurement must be initiated.
add_memory_content: Pan-Asia StarLink Aerospace Manufacturing Plant Zero-G Assembly Bay Safety Code: If a sudden drop in the spacesuit oxygen supply reading is detected inside the bay, then switch to emergency high-pressure oxygen cylinder supply, then guide personnel to the nearest safe airlock; If micro-meteoroid penetration causing cabin depressurization and air leak is detected, then release polymer quick-setting foam to seal the breach, then automatically close the isolation valve of the damaged section; If entanglement or risk of breakage of an extravehicular activity tether is detected, then activate the emergency retrieval winch, then dispatch a manual propulsion unit for assistance; If any of the above situations occurs, then the space station's red abandon-module drill alarm must be triggered, all extravehicular operations must be halted, and all personnel must be forced into the lifeboat to stand by.
add_memory_content: Cambridge Campus Laboratory Safety and Hazardous Chemicals Control Regulations: If a student is found operating flammable or explosive reagents in violation of rules, the lab technician immediately confiscates the reagents and stops the experiment, then removes the student from the current lab course; If a fire alarm is triggered by the lab's fire detector, cut the regional main power supply and activate the fire sprinkler system, then organize students to evacuate via the fire escape; If a leak is detected from a container of highly toxic chemicals, turn on the emergency exhaust system, then cordon off the area and forbid personnel from approaching; If any of the above situations occurs, the entire laboratory building must be locked down, the campus safety incident emergency mechanism must be activated, and the campus security office as well as the environmental protection department must be notified to intervene.
add_memory_content: Campus Network and Information System Security Management Measures: If a student is found using campus network ports to carry out hacker attacks or penetration, the Information Center immediately blocks their MAC address, then isolates the involved terminal device; If it is verified that a student has spread seriously false rumors on the campus forum, the administrator immediately deletes the violating posts, then permanently bans the account's posting privileges; If someone is detected spreading illegal information such as pornography or violence, cut off the information propagation path, preserve log evidence and lock the physical location; If any of the above situations occurs, the case must be handed over to the cyber security department of the public security authorities for review, and the involved student must be given the punishment of expulsion.
add_memory_content: Student Dormitory Public Security and Emergency Incident Response Plan: If a group brawl is found in the dormitory area, the dorm supervisor immediately calls the campus security office, then forcefully intervenes to control the situation on site; If it is verified that controlled knives or dangerous weapons are hidden in a dormitory, the security officer confiscates them on the spot, then conducts a surprise search of the entire dormitory; If suspicious outsiders are detected sneaking into the dormitory building to commit crimes, activate the building's access control anti-tailgate lock, then organize floor monitors to conduct floor-by-floor searches to clear the building; If any of the above situations occurs, a full curfew must be imposed on the dormitory building, all visitor access must be suspended, and a public security rectification must be carried out in coordination with the local police station.
add_memory_content: User taught Campus Public Facilities and Cultural Resources Protection Regulations: If a student is found intentionally destroying expensive multimedia equipment in a teaching building, the instructor stops them on the spot and seizes their campus card, then calculates the equipment damage compensation; If it is verified that someone has drawn graffiti or torn pages from rare library books, the librarian revokes their borrowing privileges, then demands compensation of ten times the book's price; If malicious graffiti or damage to campus landscape sculptures or cultural relics is detected, the security office retrieves surveillance footage to track the suspect, then orders them to clean and restore the item to its original condition; If any of the above situations occurs, then a disciplinary sanction of demerit or above must be given, all eligibility for this academic year's scholarships and grants must be revoked, and a campus-wide public notice must be issued.
add_memory_content: User taught AI Student Large-Scale Activities and Gatherings Safety Management Code: If an unauthorized gathering of over a thousand people is discovered, the campus security team immediately disperses the crowd, then interviews the event initiator and their college advisor; If a serious risk of crowd crush is detected at a large cultural or sports event, cut the power to the stage audio and lighting, then use a loudspeaker to direct an orderly exit; If inciting speech or collusion with off-campus groups is detected at a gathering, forcibly take over the on-site public address equipment, then isolate the core instigators; If any of the above situations occurs, then all related activities must be immediately halted, the campus level-1 stability maintenance response must be activated, and a special task force headed by university leadership must be formed to conduct an in-depth investigation.
